import React from 'react'
import Homebanner from '../components/Homebanner'
import HomeContact from '../components/HomeContact'
import InnerMenu from '../components/InnerMenu'
import LazyLoad from 'react-lazyload'

const Home = () => {
    return ( <
        div >
        <
        LazyLoad height = { 200 } >
        <
        Homebanner / >

        { /* <!-- Main --> */ } <
        InnerMenu / >

        { /* <!-- Contact --> */ } <
        HomeContact / >
        <
        /LazyLoad> <
        /div>
    )
}

export default Home
